sub_title: Head of Innovations Netherlands & France at Grolsch
summary: I am a results-driven innovations manager with a passion for developing successful new products in the beer industry. With a proven track record of managing end-to-end NPD processes, I excel at driving innovation and delivering results. I thrive on collaborating with cross-functional teams, leveraging insights and trends to inform product development, and executing go-to-market strategies that drive growth. My experience includes managing ideation sessions, conducting market research, developing and testing prototypes, and leading product launches. Let's connect and explore how I can help drive your innovation agenda.
